data.description: This property has an ASSUMABLE  loan of $663,300 at an exceptional interest rate of 5.499% which is unheard of in today's market! McGregor Reserve is HOMETOWN FAVORITE. Central location, gated security & low HOA fees. YOU’RE GOING TO LOVE this roaming, 4 bedroom plus den, 3 full bath,  pool & spa home! NEW ROOF 11/22. Beatifull  Kitchen  cabinets with   Quartz countertops,  3 car garage 20/28 House is totally handicap accessible. Large covered front porch. Exterior doors new in 2021 and light fixtures  plumbing fixtures including sinks, faucets, shower doors in all 3 bathrooms and kitchen!  New fridge with 2 ice makers, dishwasher and garbage disposal  2021 Painted inside and outside! Custom led  pool light! Several different colors and preset patterns. 12/48  porcelain tiles.  Bathroom floors are 12 by 24 travertine tiles. Main bathroom double sinks 2 large closets with dressers built in, Bidet in master toilet closet tiled walk in shower with shower door. Vanity area with cabinet and chair.  Plantation shutters.  New landscaping paved driveway,  New solar panels with backup battery to power house when the grid is down in 2022. Gutters and downspouts added in 02/23
